    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: So... you beat this silly little game about throwing slimes at pointing
    guys that took me half a year to make (truth).... was it fun? did you laugh?
    did you enjoy yourself? or are you just reading this screen. Were you satisfied
    from the ending? was leonardo di capricorn making an appearence funny? did u
    read all the screens and press all the buttons? (it's totally fine if u didnt
    btw) uhhh i kinda ran outa things to say here so uh. like and subsrcibe. if ur
    old(er) me reading this are we multimillionaires yet? (jk) uh. idk. ggs ig u
    beat the IMPOSSIBLE LEVEL OF DOOM AND DISPARE, you have earned seeing this screen.
    bye bye
